description:
The boat roads are cool, but they are useless if you can't get on them properly. This video shows you how to build and connect an Easy Loader onto your roads.

They are a simple alternative to having a boat dispenser launching section. I'll post a video on how to build a proper boat launching road section once I finish getting all the kinks out of it.
